The paper discusses Federated Learning (FL) for Internet-of-Things (IoT) devices, which involves machine learning (ML) methods and distributed computing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.IOT (Internet of Things), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture).
